The terraform scripts creates VPC, 2 public subnets (each in unique AZ), route table, attaching subnets to route table.
//usedls
Creates a S3 bucket

Creates security gooup and attache .. Creating EC2 computing instance in each AZ with particular to created vpc and subnets.

Created loab balancer, attached target groups to it . Created listerner, so tha incoming traffic form clien is allowed

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


NAt Gateway is in a public subnet. private subnet ec2 Instance ->NatGateway -> Router -> Internet Gateway.

Nat Gateway are specific to AZ, for Each AZ, we should have a NAT Gateway.


--------------------------------------------

Terraform uses modules to create multiple environments or WORKSPACE, over here, each environment has its own statefile.
